---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Medical Weight Loss - GLP-1 Resources & Providers">
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          <span class="block">GLP-1 Medical Weight Loss</span>
          <span class="block text-primary-600">Personalized Treatment & Dosage Guidance</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
          Discover how GLP-1 medications, proper dosage calculation, and comprehensive medical supervision can help you achieve sustainable weight loss while managing costs and side effects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- GLP-1 Overview Section -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Understanding GLP-1 Medications & Dosage</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 prose prose-lg text-gray-500">
          <p>
            GLP-1 (Glucagon-Like Peptide-1) receptor agonists are revolutionary medications that have transformed the approach to weight management. Our medical professionals help determine your personalized GLP-1 dosage based on individual factors and treatment goals. These medications work by:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Reducing appetite and hunger signals through precise dosage management</li>
            <li>Slowing down digestion with monitored side effect tracking</li>
            <li>Improving blood sugar levels with regular monitoring</li>
            <li>Supporting sustainable weight loss with cost-effective treatment plans</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Provider Directory -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8">Trusted Provider Directory</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Provider Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Orderly Meds</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                Trusted provider offering comprehensive telehealth services.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="https://telehealth.peptizen.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">
                  Visit Website â†’
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to Expect -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">What to Expect</h2>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <dl class="space-y-10 md:space-y-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10">
            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
                  1
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Initial Consultation</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                Meet with a healthcare provider to discuss your weight loss goals and medical history.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
                  2
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Personalized Plan</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                Receive a customized treatment plan including medication and lifestyle recommendations.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
                  3
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Ongoing Support</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                Regular check-ins with your healthcare team to monitor progress and adjust treatment.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <dt>
                <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-white">
                  4
                </div>
                <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Long-term Success</p>
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                Learn sustainable habits and strategies to maintain your weight loss results.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <dl class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                How do GLP-1 medications work?
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                GLP-1 medications work by mimicking a natural hormone that regulates appetite and digestion. They help you feel fuller longer and reduce overall food intake.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                Are these medications covered by insurance?
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                Coverage varies by insurance provider and plan. Many providers work with insurance companies and can help determine your coverage options.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">
                How long does it take to see results?
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                Many people begin to see results within the first few weeks, with significant results typically seen within 3-6 months of consistent use combined with lifestyle changes.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <div class="bg-primary-700 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="pt-10 pb-12 px-6 sm:pt-16 sm:px-16 lg:py-16 lg:pr-0 xl:py-20 xl:px-20">
            <div class="lg:self-center">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">
                <span class="block">Ready to start your journey?</span>
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-6 text-primary-200">
                Connect with a trusted provider today and take the first step towards your weight loss goals.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://telehealth.peptizen.com"
                class="mt-8 bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md shadow px-6 py-3 inline-flex items-center text-base font-medium text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50"
              >
                View Providers
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
